This patch adds the following options to the Ubuntu build script:

to install build dependencies only;
to build but not to install the generated debs;
to keep build directories from the previous run;
an ability to specify install prefix with sanity checks duplicated from bootStrap.bash to fail immediately on a bad prefix.

It also saves the messages printed to the terminal to a log-bootstrap-<DATE>_<TIME>.log file.

